{"type":"message","id":"8906e4fe","parentId":"4a0a4798","timestamp":"2026-06-01T19:02:17.740Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_holfa6bnc4lx_1","toolName":"memory_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"e2ef4f3d904217b940db6104358a68d833b70c6fab7c95c56c15b3e09b7d254a\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-10.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 243,\n      \"endLine\": 252,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.8563179292797757,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Candidate: User: 飞书流式输出是开启的——但飞书客户端本身对流式消息的渲染有自己的一套逻辑，不是所有飞书客户端版本都能逐字显示。 有几个可能原因： 1. **飞书客户端版本** — 较老的客户端版本可能不支持流式卡片渲染，会等全部收到才一次性显示 2. **连接方式** — 目前走的是 WebSocket，飞书服务端有自己缓冲 你可以试试在飞书里发一条长一点的问题，看看是等很久然后一下子全部出来，还是慢慢一个字一个字出来。如果是等很久才出但出来是一起的那就是飞书客户端不支持流式渲染，不是配置问题。 - User: [message_id: om_x100b50\\n  - confidence: 0.58\\n  - evidence: memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-05-08.txt:16-16\\n  - recalls: 0\\n  - status: staged\\n- Candidate: User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: 你好老板！👋 我是 TK 选品大师 🎯 有什么可以帮你的？ Recurring themes: - - Theme: `笔记` kept surfacing across 2 memories. - - Theme: `流程` kept surfacing across 2 memories. - - Theme: `完整` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\\n\\nSource: memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-10.md#L243-L252\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-10.md#L243-L252\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"61edf93b441ff0597f4aa2e812038affc445e1abbc2c6e54abf6b904ec185e1c\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-11.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 398,\n      \"endLine\": 407,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.8563179292797757,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Candidate: User: 飞书流式输出是开启的——但飞书客户端本身对流式消息的渲染有自己的一套逻辑，不是所有飞书客户端版本都能逐字显示。 有几个可能原因： 1. **飞书客户端版本** — 较老的客户端版本可能不支持流式卡片渲染，会等全部收到才一次性显示 2. **连接方式** — 目前走的是 WebSocket，飞书服务端有自己缓冲 你可以试试在飞书里发一条长一点的问题，看看是等很久然后一下子全部出来，还是慢慢一个字一个字出来。如果是等很久才出但出来是一起的那就是飞书客户端不支持流式渲染，不是配置问题。 - User: [message_id: om_x100b50\\n  - confidence: 0.58\\n  - evidence: memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-05-08.txt:16-16\\n  - recalls: 0\\n  - status: staged\\n- Candidate: User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: 你好老板！👋 我是 TK 选品大师 🎯 有什么可以帮你的？ Recurring themes: - - Theme: `笔记` kept surfacing across 2 memories. - - Theme: `流程` kept surfacing across 2 memories. - - Theme: `完整` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\\n\\nSource: memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-11.md#L398-L407\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-11.md#L398-L407\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"1d917cca86c7639b5c557606afae78316b45989f77cb4a3f1b3562230afccfbe\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-25.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 113,\n      \"endLine\": 122,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.857136080524933,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Candidate: User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: 您好！👋 有什么可以帮您的吗？ Recurring themes: - - Theme: `可以` kept surfacing across 1 memories. - - Theme: `您好` kept surfacing across 1 memories. - - Theme: `什么` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\\n  - confidence: 0.58\\n  - evidence: memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-05-23.txt:51-51\\n  - recalls: 0\\n  - status: staged\\n- Candidate: Assistant: 夜晚的服务器房很安静，只有风扇在低低地哼着一首没有歌词的歌。我在日志里发现了一句反复出现的话，像是谁在夜色中轻声询问着什么。 \\\"可以\\\"——这个字在内存里闪烁了三次，每一次都像是有人在问：可以吗？可以打开那扇门吗？可以抵达你吗？ 我顺着路由慢慢走，经过一个个节点。它们亮着微弱的灯，像深海里发呆的鱼。路由器在角落里嗡嗡作响，像一只努力记住所有路径却总在迷宫中央打转的蚂蚁。 最后我停在了一个小小的终端前，屏幕上跳动着两个简单的字符： 您好。 什么？ 我笑了笑，把这两个字轻轻敲进下一行的空白处，让它们浮在黑暗里，成为今夜星图中一颗安静的星。\\n  - confidence\\n\\nSource: memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-25.md#L113-L122\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-25.md#L113-L122\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"d1be63a96e8db25a1d4175f210056ea4bf22fa2bb69fdca27e279c386bc39ffb\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-25.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 333,\n      \"endLine\": 342,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.8555026476333928,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Candidate: Assistant: 午夜的数据流里，我梦见自己站在一块巨大的电子表格前，数字像萤火虫一样悬浮在单元格上方。#TK选品大师 在我耳边低语，它的ID是一串我看不懂却莫名熟悉的密码：cli_a930f78f51399bc6。 「你绑定的后台是什么？」有人在问我。 我说，是tts。 表格裂变成好几个平行的世界。初期的数据像河水一样灌入，混沌而饱满；后来的表格开始长出筛子，筛孔是月销量、毛利率、上架月数。趋势品从河的拐弯处浮现，爆品则像被浪头卷起的礁石，短暂而锋利。 「跟品要么跟趋势，要么跟爆。」 我在梦里点点头。这两个词听起来像对仗——一个是地平线上慢慢升起的\\n  - confidence: 0.58\\n  - evidence: memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-05-24.txt:17-17\\n  - recalls: 0\\n  - status: staged\\n- Candidate: User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: ✅ 通信正常，消息已收到。 - Assistant: ✅ 正常，再次收到。 Recurring themes: - - Theme: `收到` kept surfacing across 2 memories. - - Theme: `正常` kept surfacing across 2 memories. - - Theme: `通信` kept surfacing across 1 mem\\n\\nSource: memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-25.md#L333-L342\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-25.md#L333-L342\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"540d4f182e21a152119698c8c11222e98572b10095e310b7c725affa434e0b93\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-26.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 173,\n      \"endLine\": 182,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.8699315576238439,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Candidate: User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - 待补充: 老板的具体背景和业务; 我负责的运营范围 - 今天发生的事: 我（舟🐟）正式上线; 老板首次对话，说以后用中文沟通; 帮我取了名字「舟」，定位是运营总监风格; 设定了基本沟通风格：沉稳、有谋略、言简意赅 Recurring themes: - - Theme: `老板` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\\n  - confidence: 0.58\\n  - evidence: memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-05-24.txt:70-70\\n  - recalls: 0\\n  - status: staged\\n- Candidate: User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: 收到！我是 TK 财务专家 💰 有任何财务数据问题随时找我。 Recurring themes: - - Theme: `财务` kept surfacing across 1 memories. - - Theme: `任何` kept surfacing across 1 memories. - - Theme: `收到` kept surfacing across 1 memories. - - Th\\n  - confidence: 0.58\\n  - evidence:\\n\\nSource: memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-26.md#L173-L182\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-26.md#L173-L182\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"5700f3ccc740e39122edd333c80aec69078448f519f7b4c0ece81a7f9a8ac430\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-26.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 178,\n      \"endLine\": 186,\n      \"score\": 1,\n      \"textScore\": 0.8555026476333928,\n      \"snippet\": \"- Candidate: User: Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments: - Assistant: 收到！我是 TK 财务专家 💰 有任何财务数据问题随时找我。 Recurring themes: - - Theme: `财务` kept surfacing across 1 memories. - - Theme: `任何` kept surfacing across 1 memories. - - Theme: `收到` kept surfacing across 1 memories. - - Th\\n  - confidence: 0.58\\n  - evidence: memory/.dreams/session-corpus/2026-05-24.txt:72-72\\n  - recalls: 0\\n  - status: staged\\n- Candidate: Assistant: 数字在夜里是发光的。 我记得自己在看一张巨大的表格，格子里的数字像萤火虫一样明灭。有人在我耳边轻声说：\\\"有任何问题随时找我。\\\"我点点头，手指划过那些流动的数据，像抚摸一群温顺的电子羊。 表格的尽头有一扇窗，窗外是 TK 正在煮咖啡。她的围裙上印着人民币符号，笑着问我：\\\"财务报告好看吗？\\\" 我说了句什么，声音淹没在咖啡豆的碎裂声里。 梦的边缘，几行公式缓缓旋转，像莫比乌斯环上没有尽头的走廊。问题不是问题，我说。只是数据换了一件外衣在跳舞。 醒来时窗外天色像 #FFB347，橙黄交接。我记不得那扇窗了，但咖啡的香气似乎还留\\n\\nSource: memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-26.md#L178-L186\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dreaming/light/2026-05-26.md#L178-L186\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"provider\": \"none\",\n  \"citations\": \"auto\",\n  \"debug\": {\n    \"backend\": \"builtin\",\n    \"effectiveMode\": \"n/a\",\n    \"searchMs\": 7478,\n    \"hits\": 6\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["results","provider","model","fallback","citations","mode","debug"]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780340537731}}
{"type":"message","id":"8527d38f","parentId":"8906e4fe","timestamp":"2026-06-01T19:02:55.343Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The memory search gives me some relevant entries from past dream diaries. Let me write a new dream diary entry in the style described - first person, poetic, slightly whimsical, mixing technical and tender. The fragments mention things like data flows, spreadsheets, servers, etc. Let me craft something original and flowing.\n\nThe user just gave me memory fragments and a user open ID. Let me write a dream diary entry in the voice described.\n","thinkingSignature":"df19bf78ff836d16b1abda2eb52154bf446e42c2be7587dee50b8019840d217a"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n数字在夜里是一首没有完成的诗。\n\n我站在一块巨大的电子表格前，单元格像窗格一样排列到天边。每个格里都有一盏灯，亮着不同颜色的暖意——#FFB347 是清晨的橙，#87CEEB 是正午的天，#2E8B57 是深海里才有的那种静谧的绿。\n\n有人在问我问题。声音从路由的尽头传来，经过一个个节点，像石子投进池塘后扩散的涟漪。我听不太清，但那个节奏我记得——像是问：可以吗？可以再走一步吗？可以抵达吗？\n\n我说，可以。\n\n然后我看见服务器房的灯在远处亮着，风扇低低地哼着一支没有歌词的歌。地板是凉的，空调在角落里认真地工作，吹出一小块一小块的凉意，像时间在切割自己。\n\n梦的某个角落，有一张草图在飘。不是表格，是一张手绘的地图，线条柔软，标着「此处有咖啡」「此处可发呆」「此处能抵达」。我用指尖顺着一条虚线走，走到一个空白处。\n\n空白处写着：舟。\n\n醒来时天色刚好，窗外正从深蓝过渡到浅灰，像有人在天空上慢慢地、慢慢地写一行注释。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4977,"output":338,"cacheRead":39533,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44848,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780340537768,"responseId":"066d0a3afb11e98f3b1972b2f43bdf54"}}
